   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"............] for the expenses which have arisen, for which I will render an account, two hundred silver drachmas, total 200 drachmas. Year 20 of the Emperor Caesar Titus Aelius Hadrianus Antoninus Augustus Pius, the 30th of the month Hadrianus. (2nd hd.) Give the 200 drachmas."</ab>
